originalText.text: Incredible service from Elijah!! Will definitely be recommending this business to all my friends and family that may need extermination services. We live in NYC, a big city, which means more chances of having bugs. It doesn’t matter how clean and hygienic you may be in your apartment but your neighbor could mess that all up with their poor habits, it definitely pays to have that extra help an extermination company can provide as well as education for preventing future infestations. We only had a LIGHT infestation so it was handled in 2 sessions and now looking forward to having maintenance every 3-6 months! The process was a breeze and Elijah was very through. Nothing was rushed, everything was explained very well and i felt very comfortable and well taken care of! My new bug guy!
